TY  - JOUR
TI  - Natural Oligopolies
AU  - Shaked, Avner
AU  - Sutton, John
AB  - [In a market where firms offer products which differ in quality, an upper bound may exist to the number of firms which can coexist at a noncooperative price equilibrium. We fully characterize the conditions under which this possibility arises.]
